rt_taxa_interactions.Rd

Retrieve Interactions of taxon with other taxa

rt_taxa_interactions(id)

Arguments

id

integer(1)
an integer giving the id of the taxon in TaxRef (also called cdNom)

Examples

rt_taxa_interactions(id = 110335)
